description: This package is a collection of online map sources of various types: satellite, tourist, historical, and many others. If you notice any problems, please report them to the telegram chat @anygis or email anygis@bk.ru.

text:
This package is a collection of online map sources of various types: satellite, tourist, historical, and many others. 
If you notice any problems, please report them to the telegram chat.
